=== CONSTELLATION_LOCK ===
# id: 59
# title: The Constellation Lock
# chinese_title: 星座锁
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

A ceiling projector displays a star field with constellation lines missing. Tiles on the floor each bear a radical, and stepping on them in the correct order draws the constellation. The pattern must match the one shown on a faded star chart pinned to the wall.

* [Study the chart and step on the correct tiles]
  ~ gain_radical("星")
  "星" (xīng) — star, constellation
* [Use your scanner to identify the constellation]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "识" (shí) — to recognize, to know
* [Step randomly and hope for the best]
  ~ damage(5)
  "运" (yùn) — luck, fortune
